-- Fulham Signs Darren Bent on Season-Long Loan From Aston Villa
-- B y   B o b   B e n s c h
-- 2013-08-16T10:45:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-08-16/fulham-signs-darren-bent-on-season-long-loan-from-aston-villa.html
Fulham signed striker Darren Bent on
a season-long loan from Aston Villa, the Premier League soccer
clubs said on their websites.  Bent, 29, scored 36 goals in 63 games for Villa, which he
joined from Sunderland in January 2011. He’s also played for
Ipswich, Charlton and Tottenham and has scored 103 goals in 245
Premier League matches.  Bent, who has four goals in 13 games with the England
national team, will be available for Fulham’s season opener at
Sunderland tomorrow.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bob Bensch at 
 bbensch@bloomberg.net  